{"tid":2513998,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國男子以橡皮艇用16小時成功偷渡台灣 國防部長邱國正坦言海軍、海巡通報有缺失","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:44:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecb03348428686962f884a7d7113af11fd0f44b","tid":2513998,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"中國籍周姓男子4月30日從福建省石獅市駕駛具有軍規級的橡皮艇，躲過國軍及海巡署的偵蒐，橫跨台灣海峽偷渡到台中港後，遭民眾舉報後才被發現。國防部長邱國正今（3日）受訪表示，此名男子在岸上才被發現，代表在海上的偵蒐與相互通報有缺失，國防部與海巡署要把原因找出來，並逐步來改進，以彌補此缺點。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n媒體詢問，此名偷渡客是否為中共派遣特務進行測試？而未來海軍是否會增加紅外線偵蒐？邱國正說，國防部會料敵從寬，兵推用意就是用最壞的狀況來做最完善準備，每次兵推都是累積以往發掘的問題，看怎麼化解。（王烱華／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210503/YPTVZ5T3C5EOVGWUWPCLQ2H33Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210503%2FYPTVZ5T3C5EOVGWUWPCLQ2H33Y%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtQCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=97273810\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210503%2FYPTVZ5T3C5EOVGWUWPCLQ2H33Y%2F&h=c1a32901\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210503/YPTVZ5T3C5EOVGWUWPCLQ2H33Y/</a>"},{"pid":"9b5bc76d62285505d6c1db6f35d4c4294f5b43f2","tid":2513998,"uid":244809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"台灣依d防禦能力，真係守唔守到兩日...."},{"pid":"d768f39a9ab687f16168014fe19bfca1bd6a31d5","tid":2513998,"uid":275498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">坦承承認有錯</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2133b8f785442d1621eb32b2774f9f57955a2606","tid":2513998,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"阿叔+橡皮艇都咁易上到岸<br />\n如果下次係老解+登陸艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmo